# WHY: Source images are large unoptimized originals (e.g. 793KB PNG).
# Only the optimized outputs in images/ are committed.
images/source/

# Files temporarily needed by Claude Code for context
additional-context/

# External-service secrets — defensive (SPEC-004)
# WHY: These patterns guard against accidentally committing API keys, secret
# tokens, or other credentials. None of these files currently exist in the
# repo; the patterns are pre-emptive. Real values for Formspree and Turnstile
# live in their respective dashboards only — never in this repo.
.env
.env.*
*.secret
secrets/
*.key

# WHY: Working-area scratch for spec drafts (e.g., arch-review notes, design
# concept dumps). Tracked artifacts go under specs/ proper.
specs/scratch/

# WHY: Internal operator + audit docs (SPEC-017). Kept local for reference;
# removed from public repo per SPEC-017 history rewrite. Local copies live
# alongside the working tree but are not tracked. These files contain
# operator-voice notes and candid audit content not intended for public view.
OPERATOR-TODOS.md
robcparker_com_audit.md
website_audit_prompt.md

# WHY: Claude Code per-session settings (approved bash commands, MCP state).
# Already gitignored at user-global level; moved to repo-level for
# defense-in-depth so the file cannot be accidentally committed from a
# different machine or by a future contributor (SPEC-017 Pen-test G5).
.claude/settings.local.json
